Pre-Game Insights: The San Antonio Spurs look to replicate Friday night's winning effort against the Denver Nuggets.
The Spurs may be getting a little help on Saturday as forward Jeremy Sochan was upgraded from out to a game-time-decision while the Nuggets are still missing forward Aaron Gordon.
The Denver Nuggets are 3.5-point favorites and ESPN Analytics Matchup Predictor gives the Nuggets a 55.6 percent chance to pull out the victory.
